title: Microsoft Azure Storage Accounts
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the kind and location of an Azure storage account.
 Additionally the tags are displayed and the used capacity in bytes.
 You can configure levels for used capacity using the rule "Azure Storage".
 In order to use this check, you need to onfigure the Azure special agent.

item:
 The name of the resource.

inventory:
 One service is created per storage account.

